<dashboard version="1.1" theme="dark">
  <label>💬 Gemini SOC Chat Assistant</label>
  <description>Tanya langsung ke AI tentang log, payload, atau ancaman keamanan. Tidak perlu menulis SPL panjang.</description>
  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
        <style>
          .cw{font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif}
          .ch{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);padding:20px 24px;border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:18px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
          .ch h2{color:#fff;margin:0 0 4px 0;font-size:1.4em}
          .ch p{color:#7ec8e3;margin:0;font-size:.88em}
          .pills{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:10px}
          .pill{background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);color:#b0d4e8;padding:3px 11px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.78em}
          .fg{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;margin-bottom:12px}
          .fl{color:#7ec8e3;font-size:.78em;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}
          select.cs,textarea.ct{background:#0d1b22;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:6px;color:#e0e0e0;padding:9px 11px;font-size:.9em;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;transition:border-color .2s}
          select.cs:focus,textarea.ct:focus{border-color:#00b4d8;outline:none}
          textarea.ct{resize:vertical;min-height:80px;font-family:monospace}
          textarea#cp{min-height:56px;font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif}
          .grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px}
          .qrow{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:14px}
          .ql{color:#7ec8e3;font-size:.78em;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:6px}
          .qb{background:#1a2e3a;color:#7ec8e3;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:20px;padding:5px 13px;font-size:.8em;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s}
          .qb:hover{background:#00b4d8;color:#fff;border-color:#00b4d8}
          .sbar{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-top:6px}
          .ba{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00b4d8,#0077a8);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 26px;font-size:.95em;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer}
          .ba:hover{opacity:.85}
          .bc{background:transparent;color:#ef476f;border:1px solid #ef476f;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 18px;font-size:.88em;cursor:pointer}
          .bc:hover{background:#ef476f;color:#fff}
          .cc{color:#555;font-size:.8em}
          .tip{padding:12px;background:#0f2c1e;border-left:4px solid #06d6a0;border-radius:4px;color:#aaa;font-size:.85em;margin-top:14px}
        </style>
        <div class="cw">
          <div class="ch">
            <h2>🤖 Gemini SOC Chat Assistant V2.1</h2>
            <p>Paste log atau payload → pilih persona → tanyakan apa saja. AI akan langsung memberikan analisis murni.</p>
            <div class="pills">
              <span class="pill">✅ Anti-Echo V2.1</span>
              <span class="pill">✅ 5 Persona AI</span>
              <span class="pill">✅ MITRE ATT&amp;CK</span>
              <span class="pill">✅ Flexible Input</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid2">
            <div class="fg"><label class="fl">🧠 Model AI</label>
              <select id="cm" class="cs">
                <option value="gemma-4-31b-it">Gemma 4 31B IT — Recommended</option>
                <option value="gemini-3.1-pro">Gemini 3.1 Pro — Kompleks</option>
                <option value="gemini-3-flash">Gemini 3 Flash — Cepat</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="fg"><label class="fl">🎭 Persona AI</label>
              <select id="cr" class="cs">
                <option value="soc_clean_report">SOC Analyst — Laporan Insiden</option>
                <option value="threat_hunter">Threat Hunter — IOC &amp; MITRE</option>
                <option value="malware_analyst">Malware Analyst — Payload</option>
                <option value="executive_report">Executive — Level Direksi</option>
                <option value="json_extractor">JSON Extractor — SOAR Ready</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="ql">⚡ Quick Prompts</div>
          <div class="qrow">
            <button class="qb" onclick="sp('Identifikasi apakah ini brute force, password spray, atau credential stuffing. Petakan ke teknik MITRE ATT&amp;CK.')">🔐 Brute Force</button>
            <button class="qb" onclick="sp('Analisis payload ini: cari persistence, C2 communication, dan defense evasion techniques.')">🦠 Malware</button>
            <button class="qb" onclick="sp('Identifikasi semua IOC dan buat ringkasan ancaman berdasarkan data ini.')">🎯 IOC Hunt</button>
            <button class="qb" onclick="sp('Buatkan ringkasan insiden untuk CISO dalam bahasa formal, non-teknis, fokus dampak bisnis.')">📊 Exec Report</button>
            <button class="qb" onclick="sp('Analisis pola trafik jaringan ini dan identifikasi anomali yang mencurigakan.')">🌐 Network</button>
          </div>
          <div class="fg">
            <label class="fl">📋 Data Mentah (Log / Payload / JSON)</label>
            <textarea id="cd" class="ct" placeholder="Paste log, payload, atau teks mentah di sini..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="fg">
            <label class="fl">💬 Pertanyaan / Instruksi</label>
            <textarea id="cp" class="ct" placeholder="Tuliskan pertanyaan atau instruksi analisis Anda..."></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="sbar">
            <button class="ba" onclick="runChat()">🚀 Analisis Sekarang</button>
            <button class="bc" onclick="clearAll()">🗑️ Bersihkan</button>
            <span class="cc" id="cc">0 karakter</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tip">💡 <b>Tips:</b> Hasil analisis akan tampil langsung di halaman Splunk Search. Gunakan menu <b>💡 Dashboard Generator</b> di navigasi atas untuk membuat dashboard Splunk otomatis berbasis AI.</div>
        </div>
        <script>
          function sp(t){document.getElementById('cp').value=t;}
          function clearAll(){document.getElementById('cd').value='';document.getElementById('cp').value='';document.getElementById('cc').textContent='0 karakter';}
          document.getElementById('cd').addEventListener('input',function(){document.getElementById('cc').textContent=this.value.length+' karakter';});
          function runChat(){
            var d=document.getElementById('cd').value||'No data';
            var p=document.getElementById('cp').value;
            var m=document.getElementById('cm').value;
            var r=document.getElementById('cr').value;
            if(!p.trim()){alert('Harap isi pertanyaan/instruksi terlebih dahulu.');return;}
            var q='| makeresults | eval _raw='+JSON.stringify(d)+' | geminianalyze prompt='+JSON.stringify(p)+' role='+JSON.stringify(r)+' model='+JSON.stringify(m)+' | table gemini_analysis';
            window.location.href=window.location.origin+'/en-US/app/gemini_soc_assistant/search?q='+encodeURIComponent(q)+'&earliest=-1m&latest=now';
          }
        </script>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>
</dashboard>
